            <title>[LU-19781] load/unload lustre module takes long time if the large number of lnet configured</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19781</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If we have large number of LNET configured, it takes a long time to load and unload the module&lt;/p&gt;

